TextBody:
Hello Marisela,

Currently the disk space of the EPP Server is looking good, I believe that the server should be accessible.
One thing that I noticed on one of the partitions was the presence of an nginx log file, which kept increasing in size. I edited the nginx config and I removed the log file to prevent it from filling up the partition in the future.

Let me know if there is something else that I can help you with regarding this ticket.

Best regards,
Emil
